In response to: https://github.com/dotnet/aspnetcore/issues/56318#issuecomment-2361615120

`JsonUnmappedMemberHandling.Disallow` does not seem to work.

If I enable it for this object

```cs
class ExampleObject
{
	public int ExampleProperty { get; init; }
}
```

I get

```json
"ExampleObject": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "exampleProperty": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int32"
        }
    }
}
```

or an exception, depending on the way of configuration.

### Expected Behavior

